 all-level education, as well as generating visibility and high-impact pieces of news for the local and global media.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-902b9d4 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"902b9d4\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-b379b81\" data-id=\"b379b81\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8001294 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"8001294\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<style>\/*! elementor - v3.23.0 - 25-07-2024 *\/\n.elementor-widget-image{text-align:center}.elementor-widget-image a{display:inline-block}.elementor-widget-image a img[src$=\".svg\"]{width:48px}.elementor-widget-image img{vertical-align:middle;display:inline-block}<\/style>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"691\" src=\"https:\/\/www.ciahn.cl\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/3-1-investigacion-1_web.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-1628\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.ciahn.cl\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/3-1-investigacion-1_web.jpg 1000w, https:\/\/www.ciahn.cl\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/3-1-investigacion-1_web-300x207.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.ciahn.cl\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/3-1-investigacion-1_web-768x531.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/d